==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Threader
<hw>Thread"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A device
for assisting in threading a needle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A tool or machine for forming a thread on a screw or
in a nut.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Threadfin</ent>⟦br⟧
